@startuml
title E Ticketing For Bus State Diagram

[*] --> NotRegistered

state NotRegistered
state Registering
state Registered
state LoggedIn
state BookingTicket
state ManagingAccountDetails
state CheckingTicketStatus
state LoggedOut

NotRegistered : do / Create Account
NotRegistered --> Registering

Registering : do / Validate Registration
Registering --> Registered : Validation Successful
Registering --> [*] : Validation Failed

Registered : do / Login
Registered --> LoggedIn

LoggedIn : do / Check Ticket Status
LoggedIn --> CheckingTicketStatus

LoggedIn : do / Book a Ticket
LoggedIn --> BookingTicket
BookingTicket : do / Confirm Ticket
BookingTicket : do / Make Payment
BookingTicket --> LoggedIn : Successful Transaction
BookingTicket --> [*] : Failed Transaction

LoggedIn : do / Manage Account Details
LoggedIn --> ManagingAccountDetails
ManagingAccountDetails : do / Edit or Delete Account Details
ManagingAccountDetails --> LoggedIn

LoggedIn : do / Logout
LoggedIn --> LoggedOut

@enduml
